# Student Management Application

## 🧑‍🎓 Overview
A console-based Java application to manage student records efficiently using OOP principles and Java Collections.

🛠 Tech Stack
- **Programming Language:** Core Java
- **IDE:** Eclipse
- **Version Control:** Git & GitHub
- **Collections Used:** ArrayList, HashMap

## 📌 Features
- Add, update, delete, search, and display student records
- Menu-driven CLI interface
- Exception handling for invalid inputs
- Over 100 student entries handled using Java Collections
- Sorted display of students by name

## 📁 Project Structure
- `Student.java`: POJO class using encapsulation
- `StudentManager.java`: Business logic layer
- `Main.java`: CLI interface and interaction

## ✅ OOP Concepts Implemented
- Encapsulation
- Inheritance *(design extensibility)*
- Abstraction *(via separation of logic)*
- Polymorphism *(can be extended for method overriding if inherited)*

